          <p class="key-fact-body">Minimum sea-time service to reach Chief Engineer (Y3/Y2 under the legacy MCA system, now SV Chief Engineer under the 2021 MIN 524 restructure). Most engineers advance from QMED or AEC entry to Y4 in 30 months, then to Y3/Y2 with additional service.</p>
        </div>
