        <a class="profession-card" href="#income-methods">
          <div class="profession-num">02</div>
          <h3 class="profession-title">Mid-career: Y4 / SV Second Engineer</h3>
          <p class="profession-tag">"I have my Y4. I&rsquo;m Second Engineer on a 50m motor yacht. Pay is real but rotational."</p>
          <ul class="profession-points">
            <li>SV Second Engineer (post-2021) or legacy Y4 certificate holder</li>
            <li>$90K&ndash;$140K typical pay range with rotation</li>
